{"tid":2112640,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"抺茶紅豆bagel","createTime":"2020-07-17T12:52:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-22T11:38:27.000Z","uid":340796,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"42a199bd8200075ab5a758b971240f4271ba8f73","tid":2112640,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:52:15.000Z","msg":"好耐以前整過bagel 貝果, NY style 嗰隻唔啱食<br />\n或者係我唔識整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 個皮太脆, 凍咗好硬<br />\n呢排又整番, 轉咗整台式嗰隻<br />\n自己煮咗紅豆餡, 就整咗綠茶紅豆味<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C65ubFn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC65ubFn.jpg&h=71fef7ec&s={SIZE}\" />        <br />\n將所有材料混合, 搓成團狀<br />\n開頭搓完表面好岩蠶, <br />\n我就用咗中式包點的醒麵方式放佢15分鐘左右先開始搓, 就好快搓到光滑<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ENo0iko.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FENo0iko.jpg&h=5f6c8aee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YMp3f64.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYMp3f64.jpg&h=33d54dd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發酵1個鐘左右見佢大咗1倍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qUr9bFp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqUr9bFp.jpg&h=79e7372b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中佢兩野排氣, 切割分6份, 最好磅吓佢平均啲, 廢事發酵完size差太遠<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CxerdTL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCxerdTL.jpg&h=17ae5ae3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鬆弛15分鐘, 一陣整型嗰時無咁易回彈, 15 分鐘佢又大咗少少<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9DWhkyM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9DWhkyM.jpg&h=48616dda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為手得一對, 影唔到包餡整型過程, 因為包得多紅豆, 個外型唔平滑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二次發酵前<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLYPbGf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLYPbGf.jpg&h=08c90951&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二次發酵後 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OufJ0zL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOufJ0zL.jpg&h=658cac1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n煙韌外皮係因為落過滾水烚, 每面30秒, 烚完會巢皮縮水<br />\n立即入爐, <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Am5ur8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Am5ur8.jpg&h=6d0db1d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n200度15分鐘, 焗好會脹番 <br />\n今次心急焗唔夠15mins, 上色唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pt3GNdO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpt3GNdO.jpg&h=2819ceed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n老母放入爐嗰時凳咗盤包一吓, 疏咗度氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身應該會高身啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n用天然抺茶粉高溫容易走色, 我見市面都有得賣重色少少抺茶粉但未試過效果<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yinXkvP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyinXkvP.jpg&h=64671d02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n太耐無整, 麵包師可以指教吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗緊仲有咩味整 苦練吓整型技術<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2f8636d14efb78a115c60c5e3f9fc40d1e46448","tid":2112640,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:53:37.000Z","msg":"終於等到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4c17f258f543f9be22937d62351dcf1aa15a031","tid":2112640,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:53:47.000Z","msg":"好多糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8bd9d73d4a3eb7d66d7d1c25be13b6eddc5c68","tid":2112640,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:54:28.000Z","msg":"Bagel 師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7236543d712bd5815c2f2ec5a4821631a26e2cca","tid":2112640,"uid":36435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:55:10.000Z","msg":"同我整就有兩對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92fed0c3fd6a51a870cbc6fb271cfccc769994d2","tid":2112640,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2f8636d14efb78a115c60c5e3f9fc40d1e46448","tid":2112640,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:53:37.000Z","msg":"終於等到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:55:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/07.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1127d5ee2ffa7d458f3eb64df24449a1623d16a8","tid":2112640,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4c17f258f543f9be22937d62351dcf1aa15a031","tid":2112640,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:53:47.000Z","msg":"好多糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:55:52.000Z","msg":"唔夠甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f1f88c8f285ba38fe2ee0436b23dcdf85da74a","tid":2112640,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:56:03.000Z","msg":"點解要醒麵？<br />\n同埋我係咪都要買塊野黎墊住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c0bdac2f40214d9a4411ee320695d54a32bc15","tid":2112640,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7236543d712bd5815c2f2ec5a4821631a26e2cca","tid":2112640,"uid":36435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:55:10.000Z","msg":"同我整就有兩對手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:56:17.000Z","msg":"一齊搓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c19c45a188f4ca66c17a5026ddd87d2a184bd7b","tid":2112640,"uid":182683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:56:47.000Z","msg":"Bagel師<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e161e1ba2b7e9779e3c47cf567d435eb92a1113a","tid":2112640,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44f1f88c8f285ba38fe2ee0436b23dcdf85da74a","tid":2112640,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:56:03.000Z","msg":"點解要醒麵？<br />\n同埋我係咪都要買塊野黎墊住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T12:59:01.000Z","msg":"你可以唔墊, 但要之後要洗枱<br />\n搓之前其實唔洗醒, 但我發現醒一陣好搓好多<br />\n發酵完最好醒, 用途係鬆弛番麵團, 等佢造型嗰時無咁易回縮<br />\n<br />\n如果巴打你未整過麵包, 我建議你買中筋粉整吓中式包點, 求其攞肉碎做餡<br />\n失敗率都幾低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8de93aff7b0246bc2d1958fdd734b6870eb653a","tid":2112640,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T13:00:02.000Z","msg":"麵包師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d29cf2cf1d0048e03b84d365694517bf97cbfb","tid":2112640,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8de93aff7b0246bc2d1958fdd734b6870eb653a","tid":2112640,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T13:00:02.000Z","msg":"麵包師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T13:00:40.000Z","msg":"印巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d86b83b5a52f7f82f3ccba2d687401dce978cbfc","tid":2112640,"uid":246422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T13:01:43.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ebf19b7a213665648f6b9187b2dddee5991022","tid":2112640,"uid":109670,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T13:07:08.000Z","msg":"我愛un bagel"},{"pid":"adcfcf77614be1dc996b64260adda32ee8fed121","tid":2112640,"uid":308270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T13:07:09.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女朋友好鍾意食bagel，想整俾佢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2d7040e4af98c36347318acd5dd67fa88fca1f7","tid":2112640,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T13:12:32.000Z","msg":"好食<br />\n樓主好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fcab3c08680327b64d5305b8897d98ef16ed211","tid":2112640,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adcfcf77614be1dc996b64260adda32ee8fed121","tid":2112640,"uid":308270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T13:07:09.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n女朋友好鍾意食bagel，想整俾佢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T13:16:30.000Z","msg":"俾吓idea 整咩味好<br />\n過兩日會再整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de1ab006873a1ecb20312ef7b5bfa452ae5f3ee9","tid":2112640,"uid":340796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2d7040e4af98c36347318acd5dd67fa88fca1f7","tid":2112640,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,